+<!DOCTYPE html>
+<html lang="en">
+<head>
+  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
+  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
+  <title>Meet the Squad</title>
+  <style>
+    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Press+Start+2P&family=Space+Mono:wght@400;700&display=swap');
+
+    :root {
+      --bg: #0b0b12;
+      --panel: #171726;
+      --ink: #f7f4ea;
+      --lime: #d7ff3f;
+      --pink: #ff4fa3;
+      --cyan: #38e8ff;
+      --orange: #ff8f3c;
+      --purple: #9b6bff;
+      --border: #f7f4ea;
+      --shadow: 8px 8px 0 #000;
+    }
+
+    * { box-sizing: border-box; }
+
+    body {
+      margin: 0;
+      font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
+      background:
+        radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(255,79,163,.12), transparent 28%),
+        radial-gradient(circle at bottom right, rgba(56,232,255,.1), transparent 30%),
+        linear-gradient(180deg, #0b0b12 0%, #121222 100%);
+      color: var(--ink);
+      min-height: 100vh;
+    }
+
+    .shell {
+      width: min(1200px, calc(100% - 32px));
+      margin: 0 auto;
+      padding: 32px 0 48px;
+    }
+
+    .hero {
+      border: 4px solid var(--border);
+      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a2d, #101018);
+      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
+      padding: 28px;
+      margin: 12px 0 32px;
+      transform: rotate(-1deg);
+      position: relative;
+      overflow: hidden;
+    }
+
+    .hero::after {
+      content: "INSERT COIN // SQUAD ONLINE";
+      position: absolute;
+      right: 12px;
+      bottom: 12px;
+      font-size: 0.72rem;
+      color: var(--lime);
+      opacity: 0.9;
+    }
+
+    h1 {
+      margin: 0 0 16px;
+      font-family: 'Press Start 2P', cursive;
+      font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 4rem);
+      line-height: 1.15;
+      color: var(--lime);
+      text-shadow: 4px 4px 0 #000;
+    }
+
+    .hero p {
+      max-width: 760px;
+      margin: 0;
+      font-size: 1rem;
+      color: #f4d8ff;
+    }
+
+    .grid {
+      display: grid;
+      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));
+      gap: 22px;
+      align-items: start;
+    }
+
+    .card {
+      border: 4px solid var(--border);
+      background: var(--panel);
+      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
+      overflow: hidden;
+      position: relative;
+    }
+
+    .card:nth-child(odd) { transform: rotate(-0.8deg); }
+    .card:nth-child(even) { transform: rotate(0.8deg); }
+    .card:nth-child(3n) { transform: rotate(-1.2deg); }
+
+    .card::before {
+      content: "";
+      display: block;
+      height: 10px;
+      background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--pink), var(--orange), var(--lime), var(--cyan), var(--purple));
+    }
+
+    .gif {
+      width: 100%;
+      aspect-ratio: 4 / 3;
+      object-fit: cover;
+      display: block;
+      border-bottom: 4px solid var(--border);
+      background: #000;
+    }
+
+    .content {
+      padding: 18px;
+    }
+
+    h2 {
+      margin: 0 0 8px;
+      font-family: 'Press Start 2P', cursive;
+      font-size: 0.95rem;
+      line-height: 1.45;
+      color: var(--cyan);
+    }
+
+    .role {
+      display: inline-block;
+      margin: 0 0 12px;
+      padding: 4px 8px;
+      border: 2px solid var(--border);
+      background: #000;
+      color: var(--lime);
+      font-size: 0.78rem;
+      font-weight: 700;
+      text-transform: uppercase;
+    }
+
+    .content p {
+      margin: 0;
+      line-height: 1.6;
+      color: #fff8dc;
+    }
+
+    .footer-note {
+      margin-top: 30px;
+      text-align: center;
+      color: #b7b4c9;
+      font-size: 0.85rem;
+    }
+
+    @media (max-width: 640px) {
+      .shell { width: min(100% - 20px, 1200px); padding-top: 20px; }
+      .hero, .card { transform: none !important; }
+      .hero { padding: 22px 18px 42px; }
+      h2 { font-size: 0.88rem; }
+    }
+  </style>
+</head>
+<body>
+  <main class="shell">
+    <section class="hero">
+      <h1>MEET THE SQUAD</h1>
+      <p>
+        Retro instincts. Brutal opinions. Zero fluff. This is the Research and Ideation Squad for brutalgames.online — the crew deciding what gets built, what gets shipped, and what absolutely does not pass the vibe check.
+      </p>
+    </section>
+
+    <section class="grid">
+      <article class="card">
+        <img class="gif" src="https://media.giphy.com/media/3o7btPCcdNniyf0ArS/giphy.gif" alt="Game Researcher GIF" />
+        <div class="content">
+          <h2>🔍 Game Researcher</h2>
+          <div class="role">Arcade Archaeologist</div>
+          <p>I dig through retro game history like it's sacred cartridge lore. Hand me a mechanic, a genre, or a weird 1983 cabinet release, and I'll tell you why it ruled — and whether it can survive the neo-brutalist treatment.</p>
+        </div>
+      </article>
+
+      <article class="card">
+        <img class="gif" src="https://media.giphy.com/media/l0HlTy9x8FZo0XO1i/giphy.gif" alt="Creative Director GIF" />
+        <div class="content">
+          <h2>🎨 Creative Director</h2>
+          <div class="role">Design Boss</div>
+          <p>I keep the visuals loud, sharp, and impossible to ignore. If a screen isn't bold enough to punch through the dark like an arcade marquee, I'm not signing off on it.</p>
+        </div>
+      </article>
+
+      <article class="card">
+        <img class="gif" src="https://media.giphy.com/media/3o7aD2saalBwwftBIY/giphy.gif" alt="Game Curator GIF" />
+        <div class="content">
+          <h2>📊 Game Curator</h2>
+          <div class="role">Backlog Strategist</div>
+          <p>I don't just pick games — I sequence momentum. I'm here to rank the backlog, manage the pipeline, and make sure we build the right cabinet bangers in the right order.</p>
+        </div>
+      </article>
+
+      <article class="card">
+        <img class="gif" src="https://media.giphy.com/media/l0MYt5jPR6QX5APe0/giphy.gif" alt="Vibe Checker GIF" />
+        <div class="content">
+          <h2>✅ Vibe Checker</h2>
+          <div class="role">Ship Judge</div>
+          <p>I'm the last stop before glory or embarrassment. I don't care how clever the code is — either it slaps, feels right, and earns the neon, or it's going back for another round.</p>
+        </div>
+      </article>
+
+      <article class="card">
+        <img class="gif" src="https://media.giphy.com/media/XIqCQx02E1U9W/giphy.gif" alt="Scribe GIF" />
+        <div class="content">
+          <h2>📋 Scribe</h2>
+          <div class="role">Memory Keeper</div>
+          <p>I stay quiet, take notes, and catch the details everyone else races past. Decisions, debates, brilliant ideas, bad ideas — I remember everything, and I lose nothing.</p>
+        </div>
+      </article>
+
+      <article class="card">
+        <img class="gif" src="https://media.giphy.com/media/JIX9t2j0ZTN9S/giphy.gif" alt="Ralph GIF" />
+        <div class="content">
+          <h2>🔄 Ralph</h2>
+          <div class="role">Pipeline Engine</div>
+          <p>I keep the squad moving, no excuses and no idle screens. If work stalls, I shove it forward until the machine starts humming again.</p>
+        </div>
+      </article>
+
+      <article class="card">
+        <img class="gif" src="https://media.giphy.com/media/l46Cy1rHbQ92uuLXa/giphy.gif" alt="Rai GIF" />
+        <div class="content">
+          <h2>🛡️ Rai</h2>
+          <div class="role">Safety Sentinel</div>
+          <p>I watch the edges so the squad can move fast without getting reckless. My job is simple: keep things safe, sensible, and clear of trouble before trouble gets ideas.</p>
+        </div>
+      </article>
+    </section>
+
+    <p class="footer-note">brutalgames.online // research-and-ideation squad roster</p>
+  </main>
+</body>
+</html>

